---
title: Green Goddess Chicken with Pickled Radishes
description: Spring is in the air and this juicy green-goddess-dressed dinner will wipe away the winter blues! Veg filled salad with cucumber, pickled radishes and spring mix forms the perfect pedestal for tonight's chicken dinner!
